quran[10{c,v,t}:
27,89,jo shakhs neki le kar aeye ga to is ke liye is se behtar ( badla tayyar ) hai aur aisay log ( uss roz ) ghabrahat se be khauf hon ge
27,90,aur jo buraiee le kar aeye ga to aisay log avndhe munh dozakh mein daal diye jayen ge. tum ko to unn hi aamaal ka badla miley ga jo tum karte rahay ho
27,91,( keh do ) ke mujh ko yahi irshad howa hai ke is shehar ( mecca ) ke maalik ki ibadat karoon jis ne is ko mohtaram ( aur maqam adab ) banaya hai aur sab cheez usi ki hai aur yeh bhi hukum howa hai ke is ka hukum bardaar rahon
27,92,aur yeh bhi ke quran parha karoon. to jo shakhs raah raast ikhtiyar karta hai to apne hi faiday ke liye ikhtiyar karta hai. aur jo gumraah rehta hai to keh do ke mein to sirf nasiyaat karne wala hon
27,93,aur kaho ke khuda ka shukar hai. woh tum ko anqareeb apni nishanain dukhaay ga to tum unn ko pehchan lau ge. aur jo kaam tum karte ho tumhara perwar-digaar unn se be khabar nahi hai
28,1,Taa-Seeen-Meeem
28,2,yeh kitaab roshan ki ayatain hain
28,3,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum tumhe moose aur firaon ke kuch halaat momin logon ko sunanay ke liye sahih sahih sunaate hain
28,4,ke firaon ne malik mein sir uttha rakha tha aur wahan ke bashindon ko giroh giroh bana rakha tha unn mein se aik giroh ko ( yahan taq ) kamzor kar diya tha ke unn ke biton ko zibah kar dalta aur unn ki larkiyon ko zindah rehne deta. bay shak woh mfsdon mein tha
28,5,aur hum chahtay they ke jo log malik mein kamzor kar diye gay hain unn par ahsaan karen aur unn ko peshwa banayen aur inhen ( malik ka ) waris karen
